HEADWORD: Flathead
<hw>Flat"head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Characterized by
flatness of head, especially that produced by artificial means, as a
certain tribe of American Indians.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flathead</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Flathead
<hw>Flat"head`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>A Chinook
Indian. See <er>Chinook</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 1.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flat-headed</ent>⟦br⟧
